  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK509">
<l>tēṟaṟka yāraiyum tērātu tērntapiṟ </l>
<l>ṟēṟuka tēṟum poruḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let (a king) choose no one without previous consideration; after he has made his choice, let him unhesitatingly select for each such duties as are appropriate.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
